		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Heeeeey youuuuu guuuuuuuuys!!!
<br />  I'm working on a title screen using bmp2chr and Nes Screen arranger, for anyone whose worked with bmp2chr I was curious if anyone knows a bitmap to chr type program or a way to get a bmp into a chr file without the four-color-only restraint bmp2chr places on the desired input image. it can only use black white red and blue, which is lame... is there a better way to convert bitmaps into chr files??? perhaps an obvious way that's not on my radar at the moment.
<br />Thanks everyone

		

