<br />
<br />Same here. Really, YY-CHR is like the best CHR editor ever. You can draw something in MSPaint, change the colors to green,red,blue and black, and you can just copy/paste it into the editor, which is really really nice. I think those are the colors, but you have to change them most of the time.

		

